<div id="review_3480168665" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3480168665" />
    <a title="Rohan Sangodkar" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/44127106-rohan-sangodkar"><img alt="Rohan Sangodkar" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1601843530p2/44127106.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3480168665?book_show_action=true">Aug 08, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Rohan Sangodkar" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Rohan Sangodkar" href="/user/show/44127106-rohan-sangodkar">Rohan Sangodkar</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44127106-rohan-sangodkar?shelf=2020">2020</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3480168665" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15948746350992576249">1.5 stars, since a single star is only reserved for unreadable. <br/>This book is bizarre. Does not even make sense in most of the parts. Every now and then it feels like you are reading half drugged Dan Brown. The only good part I felt was that I came to know about a few of the cult groups which are spread around the world and I might further my reading about them.<br/>Not recommended unless this is the last book available. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

