    <a title="Dr. Kashmira Gohil" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/15961640-dr-kashmira-gohil"><img alt="Dr. Kashmira Gohil" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442981179p2/15961640.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3769284843?book_show_action=true">Jan 20, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dr. Kashmira Gohil" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dr. Kashmira Gohil" href="/user/show/15961640-dr-kashmira-gohil">Dr. Kashmira Gohil</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3769284843" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13819119994085742155">The book is based upon the surmise based upon author&apos;s purported long history of Christ and imagination,that Jesus was not actually dead on crucification but survived it/was alive and ventured to Shringaar/Kashmir,India, where he has long blood line after his marriage with Mary Magdalene. His tomb in Kashmir is known as Rosabal line and he has sired 03 daughters as holy trinity of Laxmi, Saraswati and Kali, each of which went to France,Japan and India. I like that author suggests that the univer</span>
  <span id="freeText13819119994085742155" style="display:none">The book is based upon the surmise based upon author's purported long history of Christ and imagination,that Jesus was not actually dead on crucification but survived it/was alive and ventured to Shringaar/Kashmir,India, where he has long blood line after his marriage with Mary Magdalene. His tomb in Kashmir is known as Rosabal line and he has sired 03 daughters as holy trinity of Laxmi, Saraswati and Kali, each of which went to France,Japan and India. I like that author suggests that the universe is based upon this holy trinity and derives its power from this female energy. But this book is filled with so much history of Jesus Christ, his blood line, angelica, basilica and all that I lost the track of story often in-between along with any interest; even from the fictional characters as father Vincent Sinclair, who was having vision of his past life as one of the living person who saw Jesus as visualised in regressive hypnosis session with his aunt Martha, the cold blooded killer Swakiki and other terrorists as Sheilkh, Galib, Albert valerio and all. Actually ,this was one of these books, I was so bored to death, I wished it to end soon. Only 02 stars.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13819119994085742155" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
